      "instruction": "<p>Once everything is ready, wash and pat the <strong>rocket</strong> dry with <strong>kitchen paper</strong></p><p>Add <strong>half</strong> of the <strong>rocket</strong> to the pesto dressing and give it a good mix up</p>",
